685
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,739
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je jedna stvar.

686
00:40:32,300 --> 00:40:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] a druga stvar je demografsko pitanje.

687
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] I poduzetnice, dakle,

688
00:40:38,099 --> 00:40:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] imaju i djecu,

689
00:40:39,519 --> 00:40:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] tako da mislim da ne moram

690
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:44,659
[SPEAKER_01] ništa dolazno objašnjavati.

691
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] I to je, dakle,

692
00:40:47,179 --> 00:40:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] osobito važno za ove žene,

693
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] za ove državu poput naše,

694
00:40:51,579 --> 00:40:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] koja je na koljenima.

695
00:40:53,039 --> 00:40:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Često puta netko me pitao

696
00:40:56,079 --> 00:40:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] šta Njemačka radi po tom pitanju.

697
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Njemačka ne radi puno

698
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] zato što ima puno više stranika.

699
00:41:03,119 --> 00:41:06,179
[SPEAKER_01] Bogati su to vam isto kao da imate, ne znam,

700
00:41:06,179 --> 00:41:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] Lamborghini,

701
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,760
[SPEAKER_01] imate, ne znam,

702
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] onaj Bentley, jel tako?

703
00:41:10,539 --> 00:41:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] I sad vas neko pita,

704
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] ovo ćeš Tesla?

705
00:41:12,079 --> 00:41:13,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naj, dobro, može,

706
00:41:13,179 --> 00:41:15,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije sad neka nužda, jel tako?

707
00:41:16,079 --> 00:41:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što je kod nas trenutno nužda

708
00:41:18,619 --> 00:41:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] i ekonomska i demografska

709
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] i upravo zato su važne žene poduzetnice.

710
00:41:23,539 --> 00:41:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Stjepan je lijepo elaborirao

711
00:41:25,659 --> 00:41:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] svoje istraživanje,

712
00:41:27,219 --> 00:41:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je taj povrat

713
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] na investiciju žene,

714
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] tako da mislim da su to

715
00:41:35,679 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] dobre lekcije za naše političare.

716
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,659
[SPEAKER_02] Stjepan, evo, imaš li još ti nešto dodati?

717
00:41:41,659 --> 00:41:44,260
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto su važne žene poduzetnice?

718
00:41:44,619 --> 00:41:45,679
[SPEAKER_02] Paziš što hoćeš reći,

719
00:41:45,679 --> 00:41:46,780
[SPEAKER_02] tu si među ženama,

720
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:49,840
[SPEAKER_02] tako da delikatne situacija.

721
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kažemo,

722
00:41:51,780 --> 00:41:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] ekonomija postoji pozitivna

723
00:41:53,019 --> 00:41:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] i normativna ekonomska analiza.

724
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] Pozitivna je ovo s brojima,

725
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] kad imate nešto konkretno,

726
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] normativna,

727
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi društvo trebalo izgledati

728
00:41:59,000 --> 00:41:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] u budućnosti.

729
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] I sad tu, naravno,

730
00:42:01,420 --> 00:42:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] se treba prvo složiti,

731
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] što je cilj?

732
00:42:03,059 --> 00:42:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] Je li cilj veća jednakost,

733
00:42:05,159 --> 00:42:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] je li cilj ekonomski rast?

734
00:42:06,500 --> 00:42:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je cilj primjerica ekonomski rast,

735
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] želiš da najbolji ljudi

736
00:42:09,460 --> 00:42:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] rade na poslove koje bi trebali raditi.

737
00:42:12,599 --> 00:42:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ja mogu reći svakako

738
00:42:16,019 --> 00:42:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] je da bi poticanje ženskog potica,

739
00:42:18,019 --> 00:42:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] što je trebalo krenuti u doslovnoj školi.

740
00:42:19,519 --> 00:42:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] I to bi trebalo postepeno ugraditi,

741
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer što su škole?

742
00:42:23,119 --> 00:42:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] Škola nije ništa.

743
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, kada bi ovako grubo rekli,

744
00:42:25,179 --> 00:42:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je tvornica ljudi,

745
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] tu prolazimo svi,

746
00:42:28,019 --> 00:42:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo prošli kroz školu

747
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:30,679
[SPEAKER_00] i dobili smo nešto

748
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] u naše razmišljene.

749
00:42:32,659 --> 00:42:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako bi trebalo poticati

750
00:42:34,039 --> 00:42:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] taj podvrdički način razmišljena.

751
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Što se tiče

752
00:42:36,599 --> 00:42:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] i nekih potpora u kratkom roku.

753
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

754
00:42:39,860 --> 00:42:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj primjer potpora što smo radili,

755
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

756
00:42:43,599 --> 00:42:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne kažem da bi trebalo napreti

757
00:42:45,460 --> 00:42:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] identičnu takvu šemu,

758
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

759
00:42:47,679 --> 00:42:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] može se toliko uboljšati,

760
00:42:48,679 --> 00:42:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno se može uboljšati,

761
00:42:49,900 --> 00:42:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je jedan dobar primjer

762
00:42:51,639 --> 00:42:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ukinut.

763
00:42:52,519 --> 00:42:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

764
00:42:53,260 --> 00:42:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] to su bile žene,

765
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] taj potpora šema žene podvrdički

766
00:42:55,860 --> 00:42:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje je vodilo ministarstvo,

767
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] podvrdično i obrata s njim,

768
00:42:58,699 --> 00:43:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] je ukinuto.

769
00:43:00,199 --> 00:43:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

770
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] postoje nekakve lokalne inicijative,

771
00:43:02,719 --> 00:43:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali koliko je meni znano,

772
00:43:05,500 --> 00:43:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] više ne postoje nacionalne razine.

773
00:43:06,900 --> 00:43:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

774
00:43:07,579 --> 00:43:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] tako nešto bi trebalo postojati,

775
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer žene imaju to ograničenje,

776
00:43:12,059 --> 00:43:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] nastavno muškaraca glede vremena,

777
00:43:13,559 --> 00:43:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] što se pričaju zbog djece,

778
00:43:15,059 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] a postoji ta nekakva psikološka literatura

779
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] koja kaže da su žene opreznije

780
00:43:19,659 --> 00:43:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad ulaze u podvrdični poduhvat

781
00:43:22,159 --> 00:43:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] i s te strane mi potreba možda nekakav savjet.

782
00:43:24,539 --> 00:43:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] I mislim da je to apsolutno dobra mjera

783
00:43:27,539 --> 00:43:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] i da bi se to trebalo poticati,

784
00:43:29,159 --> 00:43:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] a dalje potpore,

785
00:43:30,539 --> 00:43:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljimo ovim velikim iznosima,

786
00:43:32,460 --> 00:43:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] bi trebali po mojoj mišljenju

787
00:43:34,059 --> 00:43:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] biti isključivo temeljem slučnosti.

788
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali naravno,

789
00:43:38,119 --> 00:43:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] što je imala spomeno,

790
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

791
00:43:39,739 --> 00:43:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] taj problem vremena,

792
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

793
00:43:43,179 --> 00:43:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] tu bi se moglo pomoći ženama

794
00:43:46,079 --> 00:43:47,900
[SPEAKER_00] i ono možda postoji,

795
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

796
00:43:48,199 --> 00:43:49,800
[SPEAKER_00] tisuću žena

797
00:43:49,800 --> 00:43:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] koje bi bile fantasije žene poduznice,

798
00:43:51,780 --> 00:43:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisu nikad dobile priliku.

799
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] I to je onda nama trošak za duštvo.

800
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Koliki to ne mogu reći,

801
00:43:56,119 --> 00:43:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] nema nekakvog istraživanja.

802
00:43:57,239 --> 00:43:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali potencijalno postoji među ženama

803
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] neke žene koje danas rade,

804
00:44:01,539 --> 00:44:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] možda ne znam kakav posao,

805
00:44:02,780 --> 00:44:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] mogli su biti kožda fantasije žene poduznice.

806
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ovaj...

807
00:44:07,780 --> 00:44:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Trebamo ekonomski raz.

808
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:16,880
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da se svi slažemo u tome

809
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:17,360
[SPEAKER_02] i naravno,

810
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:20,960
[SPEAKER_02] nitko od žena ne traži nešto što im ne pripada,

811
00:44:20,960 --> 00:44:24,780
[SPEAKER_02] nego samo jednaku startnu poziciju.

812
00:44:24,780 --> 00:44:28,219
[SPEAKER_02] To naprosto malo više pomoći u početku

813
00:44:28,219 --> 00:44:31,340
[SPEAKER_02] da budu doista žene jednake muškacima.

814
00:44:31,460 --> 00:44:35,280
[SPEAKER_02] To je nešto prema čemu, nadam se, idemo.

815
00:44:35,280 --> 00:44:38,539
[SPEAKER_02] A što se tiče ženskog poduzetništva

816
00:44:38,539 --> 00:44:40,519
[SPEAKER_02] i mi udruzi glas poduzetnika

817
00:44:40,519 --> 00:44:42,320
[SPEAKER_02] imamo odbor za žensko poduzetništvo

818
00:44:42,320 --> 00:44:43,260
[SPEAKER_02] koje vodi Ivana.

819
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:47,420
[SPEAKER_02] Stjepan je ti si član našeg ekonomskog savjeta.

820
00:44:47,420 --> 00:44:49,980
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo, možda je to dobra podloga

821
00:44:49,980 --> 00:44:51,860
[SPEAKER_02] za jedno buduće istraživanje

822
00:44:51,860 --> 00:44:53,500
[SPEAKER_02] o ženskom poduzetništvu.

823
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo njači njegak u svoj odbor priključiti sad.

824
00:44:56,860 --> 00:45:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam slučaj za žensko poduzetništvo.

825
00:45:00,599 --> 00:45:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se bavim ekonomski tema.

826
00:45:01,679 --> 00:45:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je bilo nama ekonomski zanimljivo

827
00:45:03,440 --> 00:45:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer postoji sad ta nova literatura

828
00:45:05,619 --> 00:45:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] vezana za žene poduzetnice i za žene

829
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] općenito kako se ponašaju.

830
00:45:09,440 --> 00:45:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja sam više vako generalni ekonomist.

831
00:45:12,780 --> 00:45:14,519
[SPEAKER_02] To je baš ono što nam treba.

832
00:45:14,519 --> 00:45:15,159
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, ne?

833
00:45:15,159 --> 00:45:23,119
[SPEAKER_02] Lagano smo se približili kraju.

834
00:45:23,119 --> 00:45:26,900
[SPEAKER_02] Nadam se da vam je svima bio ugodan razgovor.

835
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:30,179
[SPEAKER_02] Nadam se i našim dragim slušateljima i gledateljima

836
00:45:30,179 --> 00:45:31,099
[SPEAKER_02] da je bilo ugodno.

837
00:45:31,099 --> 00:45:35,139
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, voljela bi još za kraj jednu misa o nešto

838
00:45:35,139 --> 00:45:38,519
[SPEAKER_02] o šim možemo završiti da ostane među svim.

839
00:45:38,519 --> 00:45:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, pogotovo damama koje nas gledaju,

840
00:45:40,559 --> 00:45:44,059
[SPEAKER_02] a i muškarcima možda da malo bolje razumiju

841
00:45:44,059 --> 00:45:46,860
[SPEAKER_02] i budu podpora svojim boljim polovicama

842
00:45:46,860 --> 00:45:49,119
[SPEAKER_02] koje se žele opušati u poduzetništvu.

843
00:45:49,219 --> 00:45:49,800
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, Ivana.

844
00:45:49,800 --> 00:45:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo, ja nekako sam naučila u svojih

845
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] koliko već devet godina poduzetništva

846
00:45:57,500 --> 00:45:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] da uvijek se nekako,

847
00:45:59,360 --> 00:46:01,239
[SPEAKER_01] situacija nam je stvarno grozna.

848
00:46:01,239 --> 00:46:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] Mi evo u vimani nadvija svaki dan čekamo

849
00:46:03,820 --> 00:46:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] na evo kad će krenuti otvaranje

850
00:46:06,739 --> 00:46:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer mi ipak imamo jako puno i venata

851
00:46:09,079 --> 00:46:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] i u njima smo ovisni.

852
00:46:10,519 --> 00:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem, nekako, uvijek ti je trenutna situacija najteža.

853
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek misliš da ne može gore,

854
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda uvijek se sve to nekako riješi.

855
00:46:22,639 --> 00:46:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjeli smo da moramo čuvati mir

856
00:46:25,599 --> 00:46:27,079
[SPEAKER_01] i mentalno zdravlje

857
00:46:27,079 --> 00:46:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] i da ćemo sve preživjeti.

858
00:46:30,239 --> 00:46:36,500
[SPEAKER_02] Slavice, misao za sve poduzetnice

859
00:46:36,500 --> 00:46:38,260
[SPEAKER_02] i one koje će to tek postati.

860
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:41,699
[SPEAKER_03] Pa ja sam se susrela,

861
00:46:41,699 --> 00:46:44,699
[SPEAKER_03] je s dosta žena što bi krenula u poduzetništvo.

862
00:46:44,699 --> 00:46:46,539
[SPEAKER_03] Međutim, njihovi je nešto kočiti

863
00:46:46,539 --> 00:46:48,860
[SPEAKER_03] kao što je, ma moram još završiti.

864
00:46:48,880 --> 00:46:51,599
[SPEAKER_03] ovo, još ću, dakle djeca malo narastu,

865
00:46:51,599 --> 00:46:53,780
[SPEAKER_03] nek sad završim još ovaj tečaj,

866
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:56,860
[SPEAKER_03] nek sad muž i nešto se sredi sa svojim poslom.

867
00:46:57,300 --> 00:46:59,179
[SPEAKER_03] nemojte to raditi s sebi,

868
00:46:59,179 --> 00:47:01,619
[SPEAKER_03] sve možete putem riješiti,

869
00:47:01,619 --> 00:47:03,460
[SPEAKER_03] samo skočite i plivajte.

870
00:47:03,460 --> 00:47:05,719
[SPEAKER_03] Ja mislim da je to jedno rješenje,

871
00:47:05,719 --> 00:47:06,619
[SPEAKER_03] nemojte pre kasno.

872
00:47:06,619 --> 00:47:09,679
[SPEAKER_03] Eto, meni je drago da sam joj ovako rano krenula.

873
00:47:12,320 --> 00:47:16,539
[SPEAKER_02] super, super, super, plivajte i s mobitelom i bez mobitela.

874
00:47:16,539 --> 00:47:18,139
[SPEAKER_02] Danira, da čujemo još tebe.

875
00:47:20,940 --> 00:47:24,559
[SPEAKER_04] Ja stvarno smatram da žene poduzetnice treba podržati,

876
00:47:24,559 --> 00:47:26,980
[SPEAKER_04] da treba imati razumijevanja za nas,

877
00:47:26,980 --> 00:47:30,460
[SPEAKER_04] jer vjerujem da ženimo stvarno genijalne ideje,

878
00:47:30,460 --> 00:47:32,340
[SPEAKER_04] genijalne inovacije,

879
00:47:32,340 --> 00:47:35,840
[SPEAKER_04] koje vrlo često ostanu zatvorene u četiri zida

880
00:47:35,840 --> 00:47:37,340
[SPEAKER_04] zbog toga što se boje krenuti

881
00:47:37,340 --> 00:47:39,320
[SPEAKER_04] i zbog nerazumijevanja okoline.

882
00:47:39,320 --> 00:47:42,239
[SPEAKER_04] Baš, da možemo biti i majke i žene

883
00:47:42,239 --> 00:47:43,719
[SPEAKER_04] i domaćice i poduzetnice,

884
00:47:43,840 --> 00:47:44,400
[SPEAKER_04] sve ujedno.

885
00:47:44,400 --> 00:47:47,739
[SPEAKER_04] Samo nam treba malo podržke.

886
00:47:47,739 --> 00:47:48,599
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je.

887
00:47:48,599 --> 00:47:49,260
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo,

888
00:47:49,260 --> 00:47:52,480
[SPEAKER_02] upravo to, upravo to,

889
00:47:52,480 --> 00:47:55,619
[SPEAKER_02] to je misao s kombiji tijela i završiti.

890
00:47:55,619 --> 00:47:58,820
[SPEAKER_02] Hrabrite svoje prijateljice,

891
00:47:58,820 --> 00:48:02,159
[SPEAKER_02] sestre, majke, čeri, žene

892
00:48:02,159 --> 00:48:06,800
[SPEAKER_02] da se otisnu te poduzetničke vode.

893
00:48:06,800 --> 00:48:09,880
[SPEAKER_02] Hrabrite im, ponavljajte da sve mogu,

894
00:48:09,880 --> 00:48:11,519
[SPEAKER_02] jer to je doista tako.

895
00:48:11,519 --> 00:48:13,599
[SPEAKER_02] A evo, već smo se i dotakli

896
00:48:13,599 --> 00:48:14,679
[SPEAKER_02] i odgoja.

897
00:48:14,679 --> 00:48:16,619
[SPEAKER_02] Stjepan je također spomenuo

898
00:48:16,619 --> 00:48:17,880
[SPEAKER_02] da sve počinje od škole,

899
00:48:17,880 --> 00:48:20,699
[SPEAKER_02] pa i odgajajte svoje kćeri

900
00:48:20,699 --> 00:48:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] onako da mogu napraviti sve što žele

901
00:48:23,519 --> 00:48:26,960
[SPEAKER_02] i postati apsolutno sve što žele biti.

902
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:29,119
[SPEAKER_02] Doista nema nikakvih ograničenja.

903
00:48:29,119 --> 00:48:31,679
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo, hvala vam svima

904
00:48:31,679 --> 00:48:33,739
[SPEAKER_02] što ste nas gledali i slušali.

905
00:48:33,739 --> 00:48:37,099
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala Ivani, Daniri, Slavici i Stjepanu

906
00:48:37,099 --> 00:48:40,639
[SPEAKER_02] i do nekog sljedećeg trenutka,

907
00:48:40,639 --> 00:48:42,260
[SPEAKER_02] do možda sljedećeg dana žena,

908
00:48:42,360 --> 00:48:43,920
[SPEAKER_02] ali nadam se i prije da ćemo se

909
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,400
[SPEAKER_02] opet vidjeti na okupu.

910
00:48:45,400 --> 00:48:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] Doviđenja.

911
00:48:47,320 --> 00:48:48,000
[SPEAKER_04] Hvala vam.

912
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:48,380
[SPEAKER_04] Čao.

913
00:48:48,380 --> 00:48:49,659
[SPEAKER_04] Čao.

